Package: infrasense
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: InfraSense Team <support@infrasense.local>
Installed-Size: 10240
Section: net
Priority: optional
Depends: postgresql-client, systemd, adduser
Homepage: https://github.com/infrasense/infrasense-platform
Description: InfraSense Platform - Infrastructure Monitoring Solution
 InfraSense is a comprehensive infrastructure monitoring platform that
 collects hardware metrics via IPMI, Redfish, and SNMP protocols.
 It provides real-time alerting, audit logging, and a web-based dashboard
 for managing and monitoring physical and virtual infrastructure.
